data.description: Always wanted to live on TOP OF THE WORLD?  Endless stars at night and the views that go on forever during the day? This is the place for you.  16.85 acres with 360 degree views---Park City Ski Mountains, Vast Mountain areas and Rockport Reservoir--views that go on forever!  This can be your year round family retreat or full time residence with cabin, several He/She Sheds (17x12, 12x12 and 12x12, two of them have heat source) plus several areas for RVs and camping spots.  (HOA said RVs can stay through summer but removed before winter).  OR, you can build that mountain top villa you always wanted.  Unlimited potential.  One owner home and he lived here full time.  Home has 1 bedroom/1 bath, large family room with wood stove (electric baseboard heat also available).  Two car detached garage (21x25 with two 7x8 doors).  Additional 7/16 shed off of the garage.  Ski/paddleboard at Rockport Reservoir or watch the Park City Balloon event from your deck.  A two-mile walking/bike trail is being worked on at this time.  2 Horses are allowed on this lot.  Park City 17 miles, Deer Valley 20 miles, Kimball Junction 19 miles, Canyons Ski Resort 17 miles, SLC Airport 44 miles.  Two photo tours for this listing, one drone footage and still photos.  Bring us your offer!
